      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such meticulous care of it, and it really shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
