    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a definitive 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The power is managed by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally optimized with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, free of imperfections, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. Every mechanical system, from the cross-drilled rotors to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard with no deferred maintenance. This is a purist-spec, investment-grade icon for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. No cosmetic wear. Single owner. Garage kept. Clean title.",
