    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-standard masterpiece that defines 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its mirror-finish paint which remains entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple and crease-free, the dashboard is pristine with no UV fading, and the original high-pile carpets have been protected since day one. Every electronic component and switch functions with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a complete, no-expense-spared service history from certified technicians. The staggered alloy wheels are flawless with zero curb rash, mounted on brand-new performance tires. This is an investment-grade vehicle that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Non-smoker, no pets, and never seen rain.",
      "price": 48500.0,
